        "_account_id": 101,
        "name": "Lai Siyao",
        "email": "lai.siyao@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "laisiyao"
      },
      "date": "2018-05-02 13:34:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nPreviously stripe_dirent_next() reads new page upon end of page, but this is not correct, so to fix, reading new page is put in a separate function stripe_dirent_load(). I've tried to make the change small, but didn't find a good way to keep the old function names.",
